Users: Soldiers of the Apokolips

Mzansi, 2079. 
You're one of the unplugged, destined for doom in a digital world where drinking water has vanished & diamonds are used to purify seawater.
To survive the apokolips you need to get your hands on as many diamonds as you can. 
Will you brave the forsaken diamond mines of the North West where the New Right and The Sultans rule?
Or will you take your chance hustling in the U.S of Africa's capital !Huigaeb? 
Beware, whichever side you choose, the trance of the diamonds reaches you in your dreams, 
your memories, invading your thoughts is the Ancient Water Spirit, 
your murky guide in this dangerous journey of #revenge, #diamonds and #corruption. 
Which path will you follow?



